STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Farad ANDREWS, a/k/a Frad Andrews, Jahad Parker, Roddy Williams, Nehemiah N. Henderson, Nehemiah A. Henderson, Dominick C. Plummer, Nahemiah Henderson, and Fard T. Andrews, Defendant-Petitioner. C-710 September Term 2018
081750 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000436-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
